##DESCRIPTION
##  College Algebra Review: Factoring quadratics with leading term 1
##ENDDESCRIPTION

##KEYWORDS('algebra', 'factoring', 'quadratic')

## DBsubject('Algebra')
## DBchapter('Basic Algebra')
